notes.name: Ruined Temple
notes.legend: Ruins of an ancient temple. Untold riches may lie within.

notes.name: Ruined Settlement
notes.legend: Ruins of an ancient settlement. Untold riches may lie within.

notes.name: Ruined Outpost
notes.legend: Ruins of an ancient outpost. Untold riches may lie within.

notes.name: Travelling Breathtaking Circus
notes.legend: Roll up, roll up, this breathtaking circus is here for a limited time only.

notes.name: Hathers Contest
notes.legend: Warriors from around the land gather for a contest of might in Hathers, with fame, fortune and favour on offer to the victor.

notes.name: Bisons migration
notes.legend: A huge group of bisons are migrating, whether part of their annual routine, or something more extraordinary.

notes.name: Teton soiree
notes.legend: A soiree has been organised at Teton as a chance to gather the foreign dignitaries of the area together to be merry, make alliances and scheme around the crisis.

notes.name: Portstabrid jamboree
notes.legend: A jamboree has been organised at Portstabrid as a chance to gather the spiritual leaders of the area together to be merry, make alliances and scheme around the crisis.

notes.name: Totham Cavern
notes.legend: The Totham Cavern. Locals claim that it is endlessly deep and unexplored.
